Yellow dresses are back after falling off the fashion scene. There is nothing like a yellow dress to give you a sparkling effect. It is the queen of colours at the moment. Yellow fabrics are in a class of their own.  Whether as a top or gown, it’s now a must-have item among young and old fashionistas. There is no doubt it is the hottest dress for the season, it’s hot and haute. The designs and artwork on most of these dresses are sexy, classic and stylish. The embellishments and detail add just the right touch. They are everywhere and in several imaginative styles and fabrics that include flirty eyelets to well tailored dinner gowns. Stylishly design yellow outfit will look great on any jeans, trousers or skirt.  And you can add a touch of class to it if the dress spots a sequence, stones, beads and other colourful accessories. Yellow wears can be used to dress up or down, it all depends on the design, occasion and the way they are combined.